{"tid":2035594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭重臨，需要大家嘅創意？？討論>組隊>行動","createTime":"2020-05-26T04:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:58:21.000Z","uid":56311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce345616b7571a1aba960500a346718828c69d80","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdJv7iG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdJv7iG.png&h=4dbaeae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前<br />\n黑簡迪巴之前有個關於創意嘅post，我覺得佢講得好啱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2023929/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2023929/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而家國安法殺到，抗爭之火將要重燃，我地應該發掘多啲抗爭手法，以突破重圍。<br />\n<br />\n而其實要發揮創意並唔難。<br />\n<br />\n一日有24小時，如果每人每小時可以產生0.01個新idea，200萬人每日就有48萬個新idea，只係平時我地不以為然，跟住過兩日就唔記得左個idea。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>所以我特登搞左個Brainstorm平台，比大家將自己嘅idea放上去，集思廣益。（任何有助光復香港嘅idea都可以）<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭Brainstormer: <a href=\"http://t.me/hkbrainstormer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkbrainstormer&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=1d3b87fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkbrainstormer</a><br />\nIdea投稿:<br />\n <a href=\"http://t.me/hkbrainstormbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkbrainstormbot&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=382e0e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkbrainstormbot</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n得閒又可以睇下其他人嘅idea，話唔定睇睇下你又會諗到啲新野。如果見到高質idea，亦可以響channel discussion傾下點實行。<br />\n<br />\n大家唔洗怕羞，咩idea都可以放上嚟，最重要嘅係推動思考同討論。如果傾出實際可行嘅idea，提議者可以另開tg gp開始進行實質籌備，並於連登宣傳，如有需要，admin可以提供援助。<br />\n<br />\n大家加油，一齊用創意對抗極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8592217e4a121ee4be9b801816820ae408c4d2c5","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無可否認,連登已經唔係上年咁可以咁容易討論組織班人做嘢,個平台成立就係希望歡迎唔同諗法人可以組織一齊,各方面出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有懷疑歡迎起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d76fabc6cc7a5efe24db8a6962be010410474af8","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"632e7b9ff41eefcb4e82c1583e2e51c71f316caf","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d9739fe1935faab16e0a81153b1276a39b5b16c9","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"dc46885f2a9e6e5ed05293541203a73ba6accc05","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fc076feaa989f306308b63408c6d4c0c107b2978","tid":2035594,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673ecafdf3614a92324f301f0e43cc7d180c9ad1","tid":2035594,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"一齊去貼文宣啦!<br />\n借推!<br />\n<br />\n無論之後嘅香港會點, 希望大家都唔好放棄文宣, 一齊去做貼紙師!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035600</a>"},{"pid":"11e674785db0f02c7a4bdc7f1ff8f2672729b70f","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"ba110c792e1e630f57c1c74ad83be89ed626b328","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d2313d43cc373ec393df0892c9fae882e6ff9578","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"例如：成立一team 人專幫冇連登ac 人開post嘅,俾其他參與呢場抗爭人都可以上黎出聲etc..<br />\n拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145c5ac4f01fd4b7273e58ad185eb60fbea23b9a","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ba4793417b85f9c16264f4d529160a597fd413f3","tid":2035594,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"8"}]}